description: Try our easy to follow Speedy Thai Green Curry With Chicken & Veg recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Green curry,Broccoli,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Spring,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Wheat free,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Speedy Thai Green Curry With Chicken & Veg Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400g RSPCA-approved chicken thigh fillets, roughly chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Heat 1 tbs vegetable oil in a large, deep frying pan over medium-high heat. Cook chicken, stirring, for 5 minutes or until browned.
Add curry paste and cook, stirring, for 1 minute or until fragrant.
Add coconut milk and bring to the boil. Reduce heat to medium and simmer for 5 minutes or until slightly thickened.
Add vegetables and reduce heat to low. Simmer for 5 minutes or until vegetables are tender. Serve.
